DIGEST
SB 40 Original 2026 Regular Session Wheat
Present law provides for the procedure for approaching authorized emergency vehicles
parked on the side of the highway. Proposed law adds a reference to the definition of an
authorized emergency vehicle.
Present law provides for the procedure for approaching vehicles that are not authorized
emergency vehicles parked on the side of the highway. Proposed law adds a reference to the
definition of vehicle.
Proposed law specifies the color of lights for authorized emergency vehicles.
Proposed law provides for technical matters.
Proposed law provides for the department to promulgate rules in accordance with the law.
Effective August 1, 2026.
(Amends R.S. 32:125)
